game.name: Frogger Jump
game.description:
This cute and little frog looks very scared and is unable to find the way to his home. So, he is seeking for someone who can guide him to make a way towards his place. Do you think that you are capable enough to assist this lovely frog? Join Frogger Jump and get ready to show off your intense jumping skills to navigate multiple platforms! Timely jump would be a key to win in this cute free online adventure challenge. 

The problem is that not only one frog needs your guidance, but there are five frogs that need your supervision. Control the jumping of all the frogs and get ready to avoid all the obstacles that come on their way. Your focus should be to make sure that they all reach to the end safely without being hit or fall down in any gap between the platforms. Try to collect all the frogs you see on the platforms and also check if they do not hit or jump on each other in this html5 jumping game!

There are now three different environments including Grass, Winter and Dessert to play with. You can unlock the next environment only if you have cleared all the stages of the previous one. Each environment has 6 stages to complete for players. Click the LMB or tap the screen to make your frogs jump from one platform to the other! All the best to guide all the frogs jump safely to the other side in our free animal skill game! Play top adventure games online on atmegame.com and have a blast alone or with your friends without download!!
